  • General Features:

  • 20MHz & 40MHz & 80MHz bandwidth transmission
  • Complies with IEEE 802.11ac, IEEE 802.11n, IEEE 802.11g, IEEE 802.11b standards

  • Support STBC, Transmit Beamforming

  • 2.412 - 2.483.5GHz
  • 4915-5825GHz
  • RF Output Power (Typical):
  • 802.11n: 13±1dBm
  • 802.11g: 13±1dBm
  • 802.11b: 15±1dBm
  • 802.11a: 16±1dBm

  • 11a (433M):-78±1dBm @ 10% PER,
  • 11n (150M) : -72±1dBm @ 10% PER
  • 11g (54M): -75±1dBm @10% PER
  • 11b (11M): -87±1dBm @8% PER
  • Radio Type:
  • IEEE 802.11b: DSSS(CCK/DQPSK/DBPSK)
  • IEEE 802.11g: OFDM(64-QAM, 16-QAM, QPSK, BPSK)
  • IEEE 802.11n: OFDM(BPSK/QPSK/16-QAM/ 64-QAM)
  • IEEE 802.11a: DSSS(CCK/DQPSK/DBPSK)
  • Data Rate:
  • 11n: 135/121.5/108/81/54/40.5/27/13.5Mbps 130/117/104/78/52/39/26/13Mbps 65/58.5/52/39/26/19.5/13/6.5Mbps
  • 11g: 54/48/36/24/18/12/9/6M(adaptive)
  • 11b: 11/5.5/2/1M(adaptive)
  • 11a: 433 max
  • Transmitting Distance:
  • Indoor: 30 meters (98-feet)
  • Outdoor: 100 meters (328-feet)
  • Security Mode:
  • 64/128/152bit WEP
  • WPAPSK
  • WPA2PSK
  • WPAPSK/WPA2PSK
  • Dimensions:
  • 0.2 x 0.7 x 2.6-inches (H x W x D, approximate)
  • MediaTek MT7610U 600Mbps Wireless-AC 2.4GHz/5GHz Dual Band USB 2.0 Adapter
  • Quick Installation Guide
  • 3-inch Drive CD

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
